Dialogue: 0,1:37:15.86,1:37:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}很棒唷..
Dialogue: 0,1:37:21.73,1:37:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}真淫荡啊..
Dialogue: 0,1:37:28.94,1:37:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好害羞..
Dialogue: 0,1:38:14.18,1:38:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\b1\fn华文楷体\fs20}好害羞..
